titles.title: Directing the Speaker to administer the oath of office to the representative-elect from the 13th Congressional District of Michigan.
Directing the Speaker to administer the oath of office to the representative-elect from the 13th Congressional District of Michigan.

action.text: Mr. Levin asked unanimous consent to consider as introduced.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: Directs the Speaker of the House of Representatives to administer the oath of office to Representative-elect Brenda Jones from the 13th congressional district of Michigan.
